<pre><code class='hljs language-mdx'><span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>abbr</span> <span class='hljs-attr'>title</span>=<span class='hljs-string'>'Graphics Interchange Format'</span>></span></span>GIF<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>abbr</span>></span></span> is a bitmap image format.

H<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>sub</span>></span></span>2<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>sub</span>></span></span>O X<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span>n<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span> + Y<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span>n<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span> = Z<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span>n<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span>

Press <span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span>CTRL<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span> + <span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span>ALT<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span> + <span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span>Delete<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span> to end the session.

Most <span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>mark</span>></span></span>salamanders<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>mark</span>></span></span> are nocturnal, and hunt for insects, worms, and other small creatures.

~~strikethrough~~
</code></pre>
<p><abbr title='Graphics Interchange Format'>GIF</abbr> is a bitmap image format.</p>
<p>H<sub>2</sub>O X<sup>n</sup> + Y<sup>n</sup> = Z<sup>n</sup></p>
<p>Press <kbd>CTRL</kbd> + <kbd>ALT</kbd> + <kbd>Delete</kbd> to end the session.</p>
<p>Most <mark>salamanders</mark> are nocturnal, and hunt for insects, worms, and other small creatures.</p>
